text: Ðis sind ða landgemæra to ðan X hidan æt Hæsellea to ðan nyðran tune.
Ðæt andlang wicgan dic ðæt hit sticað on wearra ford.
Swa andlang mores oð ðene bradan herepað.
Ðæt on ðæra æcera heafada ðæt hit sticað on Humbra.
Andlang Humbra ðæt on roppan broc foron ongean stangedelf.
Eft andlang roppan broces ðæt hit cimð on roppan ford ðær hit ær onfeng.
